data.description: Enjoy deep water RIVERFRONT lifestyle with this beautifully renovated home on Ribault River! Ready for move in, featuring all new:  Roof, Kitchen, Baths, Freshly Painted Interior, New Garage door & Liftmaster auto opener, Water Heater, refinished hardwood floors, carpeted bedrooms & more! Waterfront views from master suite, two bedrooms & den.  Exterior features a large back yard with a brand new deck for enjoying cookouts or just relaxing above the river.  This home did not flood in the historic flooding of Hurricane IRMA!  This beautiful move-in ready home won't last very long.  Call TODAY for more information or for your viewing appointment!
